  "detailed_description": "\"In the Dark\" is a roguelike deck-building horror card game. Collect cards, skills, items, and souls, and use them to survive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/eae4d861b51941c81b32bef8dbdd967b.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br>The world was shrouded in darkness due to the impact of the meteorite, monsters have appeared, and corpses have turned into zombies. The only way to survive is to move on. Select one of three places.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/3490c483a644add6f38876d2c2a0e883.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>You can cooperate with and fight against other survivors.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/9dbd2b3cc3aeb5bd0a57020a77170ae8.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>Whenever you enter safe areas alone, ghosts will appear. In addition...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/ff13f596b342468639b25c8aad1086f8.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=240 /></span><br>A horde of zombies is a formidable foe.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/051059ffedc08738fd37f6dd540db6c4.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>Defeating a boss monster, you can choose to end the play or continue. You should consider your free time and achievements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/309d8d64e80536312177a8c88c3fbb2c.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"In the Dark\" is a roguelike deck-building horror card game. Collect cards, skills, items, and souls, and use them to survive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/eae4d861b51941c81b32bef8dbdd967b.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br>The world was shrouded in darkness due to the impact of the meteorite, monsters have appeared, and corpses have turned into zombies. The only way to survive is to move on. Select one of three places.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/3490c483a644add6f38876d2c2a0e883.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>You can cooperate with and fight against other survivors.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/9dbd2b3cc3aeb5bd0a57020a77170ae8.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>Whenever you enter safe areas alone, ghosts will appear. In addition...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/ff13f596b342468639b25c8aad1086f8.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=240 /></span><br>A horde of zombies is a formidable foe.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/051059ffedc08738fd37f6dd540db6c4.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>Defeating a boss monster, you can choose to end the play or continue. You should consider your free time and achievements.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/309d8d64e80536312177a8c88c3fbb2c.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span>",
